triangle3d_plotly(pred, targ=None, labels=['x', 'y', 'z'], show_axes=True, show_bounds=True, cmap='jet')

class TrianglePlotBokeh[source]

TrianglePlotBokeh(pred:ndarray, targ:ndarray, labels:list=['0', '1', '2'], show_bounds:bool=False, urls:list=None)

This gives a 2d plot with image tooltips when the mouse hovers over a data point.

class VizPreds[source]

VizPreds(method=TrianglePlotBokeh) :: Callback

This fastai callback is designed to call the bokeh triangle plot with each batch of training, using validation data.
